    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a reliable ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner right away! Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s perfect for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle without the 'new car' price tag. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
