    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example benefits from documented preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a serviced double-VANOS system to ensure optimal cam timing. The M-variable limited-slip differential provides exceptional power delivery out of corners, while the chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity. Though the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains robust with excellent compression and a crisp throttle response. It is a purist-spec driver\u2019s car with all major mechanical hurdles addressed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
