    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, offering a harmonious blend of reliability and refined style. The exterior remains striking, with the original paint holding a deep, reflective gloss that highlights the car's clean lines. While there are a few negligible stone chips on the lower front valance consistent with careful highway use, the body is remarkably straight and free of significant blemishes. Step inside to find an interior that has been treated with the utmost respect; the leather seating is supple and well-conditioned, showing only light softening on the driver's bolster, and the cabin remains entirely smoke-free. All electronic components, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and reflects a rigorous maintenance history. It has been serviced exclusively with synthetic oils, and the most recent inspection confirmed that the brakes and suspension are in excellent working order. The tires have ample tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and quiet ride from the moment you take the keys. This car represents a perfect opportunity for a buyer seeking a turn-key vehicle that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained to ensure both mechanical reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior retains a professional luster, complemented by an interior that reflects attentive care and minimal wear. Engineered for the discerning driver, this model offers a refined performance profile and remains a testament to its manufacturer's standards. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a well-preserved vehicle that balances sophisticated styling with proven durability.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in great shape! It runs smoothly, looks sharp, and is honestly just a joy to drive. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, it's got plenty of life left in it. I've taken really good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great new home. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, known for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and an M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque distribution. Mechanically sound, the double-VANOS system has been serviced, and the chassis has been enhanced with professional rear subframe reinforcement and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering the tactile steering feedback and linear power delivery that define this chassis. It remains a balanced, visceral performance machine ready for the canyon or the track.",
